  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of the study is to assess autonomic nervous system and cardiovascular controll&#xD;
      during orthostatic challenge in 90 patients recovered from COVID-19 and devided into three&#xD;
      groups depend on severity of the morbidity.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
